author: Nerdrotic
description:
A completion chronicling the last 4 years leading to the demise of a once proud America institution.
Hollywood was once a place of wonder and imagination that brought people of all makes, shapes, and sizes together.
Now it is one of the most divisive entities in America culture, and that's a bad thing. 

Edited by@PierryChan and @QTRBlackGarrett
title: The Decline and Fall of Woke Hollywood
